No. 65,

Orig.

Texas v. New Mexico. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 454 U. S. 1076.]

Report of the Special Master received and ordered filed. Exceptions to the Report, with supporting briefs, may be filed by the parties within 45 days. Replies to such Exceptions, with supporting briefs, may be filed within 30 days.
